summary: A new custom race created from hours of listening to Reactor7x & Aesthetic Perfection.
descriptionHtml:
This is purely aesthetic for now. I love creepy shit. I love monsters. And many people who know my true intentions and personality would call me 'evil' (yet I'm one of the sweetest, nicest people you'll ever meet).

So, I get distracted a lot. This is one of those distractions.

Just female for now, sorry. This is just for fun. I'll probably create a male counterpart once I start working on the male version of GCO.
